# .editorconfig
# 团队统一编码配置 - 所有主流编辑器都会自动读取此文件
# 支持: VS Code, Visual Studio 2019+, JetBrains 系列, Sublime Text 等

root = true

# 所有文件的默认设置
[*]
charset = utf-8-bom
end_of_line = crlf
indent_style = space
indent_size = 4
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
insert_final_newline = true

# C++ 源文件
[*.{cpp,h,hpp,c,cc,cxx}]
charset = utf-8-bom
indent_size = 4

# CMake 文件
[CMakeLists.txt]
indent_size = 4

[*.cmake]
indent_size = 4

# JSON 配置文件
[*.json]
indent_size = 2

# Markdown 文档
[*.md]
trim_trailing_whitespace = false

# Shell 脚本 (如果有 Linux/Mac 队友)
[*.sh]
end_of_line = lf
charset = utf-8
